item.title: Prayer bpn10243 in Māori
item.description: Korōria ki a Koe e tōku Atua! Ko ahau tētahi o ō pononga, mea whakapono ki a Koe me Ō tohu. e kite nei Koe i tāku whakaahu i ahau ki te kūaha o Tōu atawhai, i tāku takahuri i tōku kanohi ki te ahunga o Tōu tohu atawhai. Ko tāku inoi ki a Koe, mā Ōu ingoa hirahira rawa, me Ōu tūāhua o runga rawa, kua whakatūwhera ki tōku kanohi ngā kūwaha o Āu tākoha.
